08:31.000 --> 08:38.000
A small example of the responsibility for the value of the indicator is the undesirable flow of personnel.

08:38.000 --> 08:50.000
Imagine that the financial director of a company receives information from the manager on the personnel via email.

08:50.000 --> 08:52.000
Here is the content.

08:52.000 --> 09:04.000
The manager, digging on the Internet, found a resume of an employee who works in an accounting firm subordinate to the financial director.

09:04.000 --> 09:06.000
She is secretly looking for a job from the employer.

09:06.000 --> 09:16.000
The task of the HR is to periodically look on the Internet and see if the employees are looking for a job in secret from the employer.

09:16.000 --> 09:22.000
So, the resume of one employee was found on one of the sites, and she is looking for a job.

09:22.000 --> 09:30.000
HR informs the financial director that her subordinate is trying to find a job in secret from the employer.

09:31.000 --> 09:35.000
The financial director calls her subordinate and asks her,

09:35.000 --> 09:42.000
Masha, we found your resume on the Internet, you are looking for a job in secret from us.

09:42.000 --> 09:45.000
What happened? What is wrong? What are the problems?

09:45.000 --> 09:49.000
Masha asks, are you satisfied with my work?

09:49.000 --> 09:54.000
The financial director says, yes, Masha, we are very satisfied with your work, you are a great fellow.

09:55.000 --> 10:00.000
You are doing great in your journal No. 7, which we entrusted you with.

10:00.000 --> 10:04.000
We have big plans and visions for you, you are our personnel reserve.

10:04.000 --> 10:10.000
We hope that you will develop very well in our company.

10:10.000 --> 10:14.000
Masha asks, please tell me about the level of salary that you offer me.

10:14.000 --> 10:19.000
How much does it compensate my efforts?

10:19.000 --> 10:25.000
The financial director says, I am sorry, Masha, I don't know how much your experts earn in the market.

10:25.000 --> 10:31.000
If this amount is not enough for you, why didn't you come and tell me that you are not enough,

10:31.000 --> 10:36.000
I think I should earn more, I would gladly raise your salary.

10:36.000 --> 10:42.000
You should have told me about it. I think that if people don't ask, they are satisfied.

10:42.000 --> 10:46.000
Masha says, my parents raised me differently.

10:46.000 --> 10:49.000
They told me that I shouldn't ask, I should work well,

10:49.000 --> 10:53.000
