11:37.000 --> 11:46.000
I think that HR's task is not only to sit on the Internet and look at the results.

11:46.000 --> 11:52.000
Ideally, HR should have drawn a portrait of Masha for her direct manager and told the financial director,

11:52.000 --> 11:56.000
Masha is specific, she won't ask.

11:56.000 --> 12:02.000
And the second thing is the level of salary in the market for such specialists.

12:03.000 --> 12:05.000
